model_str:
ProgressiveModel(
  (blocks): ModuleList(
    (0): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2d(3, 54, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (1): BatchNorm2d(54, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (2): ReLU()
      (3): Dropout2d(p=0.2, inplace=False)
      (4): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
    (1): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2d(54, 140, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (1): BatchNorm2d(140, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
      (2): ReLU()
      (3): Dropout2d(p=0.2, inplace=False)
      (4): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
    )
  )
  (global_pool): AdaptiveAvgPool2d(output_size=1)
  (extra_proj): Sequential(
    (0): Linear(in_features=0, out_features=32, bias=True)
    (1): ReLU()
    (2): Dropout(p=0.3, inplace=False)
  )
  (classifier): Sequential(
    (0): Dropout(p=0.2, inplace=False)
    (1): Linear(in_features=140, out_features=2, bias=True)
  )
)
